# Integration Status Dashboard

**Format:** Google Sheet or Excel  
**Update Frequency:** Every Monday  
**Share With:** Client (view-only), Dev team (edit access)  
**Purpose:** Single source of truth for integration progress

---

## How to Use This

1. Copy this template to Google Sheets or Excel
2. Fill out all integrations needed at project start
3. Update status every Monday (or when status changes)
4. Share view-only link with client in weekly update
5. Reference in status meetings

---

## Template Structure

### Column Definitions

| Column | Values | Purpose |
|--------|--------|---------|
| Integration Name | Service name | What integration this is |
| Status | Not Started / In Progress / Waiting on Client / Waiting on Provider / Blocked / Complete | Current state |
| Owner | Client / Us / Dev / Provider | Who's responsible |
| Blocker | Text description or "None" | What's preventing progress |
| Next Action | Specific action needed | What needs to happen next |
| Target Date | MM/DD/YYYY | When this should be complete |
| Actual Date | MM/DD/YYYY | When it was actually completed |
| Notes | Text | Additional context |

---

## Status Definitions

**Not Started** = Haven't begun setup yet (usually means it's scheduled for later)

**In Progress** = Actively being worked on (accounts created, configuring settings)

**Waiting on Client** = Need something from client before we can proceed
- Examples: DNS access, credentials, approval, decision

**Waiting on Provider** = Waiting on external service
- Examples: DNS propagation (48hrs), Google OAuth approval (1-3 days), domain verification

**Blocked** = Cannot proceed due to issue
- Examples: Account locked, service down, technical limitation discovered

**Complete** = Fully configured and tested in all environments
- Must be tested in dev, staging, and production before marking complete

---

## Example Dashboard

| Integration | Status | Owner | Blocker | Next Action | Target | Actual | Notes |
|-------------|--------|-------|---------|-------------|--------|--------|-------|
| Resend Email | Waiting on Provider | Client | DNS propagating | Wait 24 more hours | Jan 22 | - | Added DNS records Jan 20 |
| Google SSO | In Progress | Dev | None | Configure redirect URLs | Jan 21 | - | OAuth consent screen approved |
| Supabase DB | Complete | Dev | None | - | Jan 18 | Jan 18 | Schema reviewed with client |
| Stripe Payment | Not Started | Client | Account not created | Client to create Stripe account | Jan 25 | - | Will set up Week 3 |
| Push Notifications | In Progress | Us | None | Set up Firebase project | Jan 23 | - | Client provided bundle IDs |
| Linqly Deep Links | Waiting on Client | Client | App not published yet | Wait for App Store approval | Jan 30 | - | Can't test until app published |

