## Color Coding (If Using Spreadsheet)

**Status Colors:**
- üü¢ Complete = Green
- üü° In Progress = Yellow  
- üî¥ Blocked = Red
- ‚ö™ Waiting on Provider = Light gray
- üü† Waiting on Client = Orange
- ‚ö´ Not Started = White/no color

**Owner Colors:**
- Client = Light blue
- Us = Light green
- Dev = Light yellow
- Provider = Light gray

This makes it easy to scan and see: "Oh, 3 items waiting on client, 1 blocked, 2 in progress"

